sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 👤 Customer
    participant POS as POS Page
    participant SS as Sales Service
    participant FS as Finance Service
    participant PG as Payment Gateway<br/>(VNPay/MoMo/...)
    participant DB as Database

    POS->>SS: createPayment(orderId, amount, method)
    SS->>PG: createTransaction(orderId, amount, returnUrl)
    PG-->>SS: { paymentUrl, txnId }
    SS-->>POS: { paymentUrl, txnId }
    POS->>U: Hiển thị QR / redirect tới paymentUrl
    U->>PG: Nhập thông tin thanh toán
    PG->>PG: Process payment
    PG-->>U: Redirect về returnUrl với status

    Note over PG,SS: Async IPN (Instant Payment Notification)
    PG->>SS: POST /webhook/payment/<gw><br/>{ orderId, amount, status, signature }
    SS->>SS: Verify HMAC signature
    SS->>SS: Verify timestamp (anti-replay)
    SS->>DB: Lookup order
    SS->>DB: UPDATE invoice SET status=paid
    SS->>FS: Sinh phiếu thu cashbook
    FS->>DB: INSERT cashbook
    SS-->>PG: 200 OK
    SS->>POS: WebSocket / poll → notify success
    POS->>U: ✅ Thanh toán thành công
